<!-- ══════ HERO ══════ -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="hero-birds-bg"></div>
  <div class="about-hero-content">
    <div class="eyebrow">🌍 Our story</div>
    <h1>We believe learning has<br/><em>no barriers.</em></h1>
    <p>BridgeUp was founded with one conviction: every person — regardless of ability — deserves access to quality education, therapy, and community. We build the bridge.</p>
    <div class="hero-stat-row">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-n">2022</span>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">Founded in Cairo</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-n">4,200+</span>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">Learners served</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-n">85</span>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">Partner centers</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <span class="hero-stat-n">6</span>
        <div class="hero-stat-l">Disabilities supported</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width:100%;display:block">
      <path d="M0,30 C240,60 480,0 720,30 C960,60 1200,0 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,.5)"/>
      <path d="M0,45 C360,15 720,60 1080,35 C1260,22 1380,50 1440,45 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#fff"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ OUR STORY ══════ -->
<section class="story-section">
  <div class="story-grid">
    <div class="story-visual">
      <div class="story-card-main">
        <h3>Where it started 🌱</h3>
        <p>BridgeUp was born from a simple frustration: parents of children with disabilities had nowhere to turn for clear, accessible, and trusted guidance. Therapy centers were hard to find. Courses weren't designed for their children. Support was scattered and inconsistent.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px">We decided to change that.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-float">
        <div class="sf-icon">💡</div>
        <div><div class="sf-t">Founded in Cairo</div><div class="sf-s">By educators & therapists</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-float">
        <div class="sf-icon">🏆</div>
        <div><div class="sf-t">Top EdTech 2025</div><div class="sf-s">Arab EdTech Association</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-text">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal">Our journey</div>
      <div class="section-title reveal">Built by people<br/>who care deeply.</div>
      <p class="reveal">In 2022, a small team of special education teachers, certified therapists, and accessibility researchers came together in Cairo. They had all seen the same gap — brilliant, capable people with disabilities left behind by a system not built for them.</p>
      <p class="reveal">They started by mapping every therapy center in Egypt. Then building a course library. Then adding sign language tools. Then partnering with schools. One step at a time, BridgeUp grew into a full platform — but the mission never changed.</p>
      <p class="reveal">Today BridgeUp serves over 4,200 learners across Egypt and the Arab world, and we're just getting started.</p>
      <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:28px">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.location='signup.html'">Join our community →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ MISSION & VISION ══════ -->
<section class="mv-section">
  <div class="mv-inner">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal">What drives us</div>
      <div class="section-title reveal">Mission & Vision</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mv-grid">
      <div class="mv-card mission reveal">
        <span class="mv-card-icon">🎯</span>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>To bridge the gap between people with disabilities and the educational, therapeutic, and social resources they need — through accessible technology and a compassionate, expert community.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-3)">We do this by building tools that put the user first, partnering with the best certified professionals in Egypt, and never compromising on quality or inclusion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mv-card vision reveal">
        <span class="mv-card-icon">🔭</span>
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>A world where disability is never a barrier to learning, growth, or belonging. We envision an inclusive Arab society where every person's potential is recognized, nurtured, and celebrated — regardless of their ability.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-3)">We imagine a future where a child with Down Syndrome, a Deaf adult, and a parent raising an autistic child all find exactly what they need — in one warm, trusted place.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ VALUES ══════ -->
<section class="values-section">
  <div class="values-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">What we stand for</div>
    <div class="section-title reveal">Our Core Values</div>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">Everything we build, every decision we make, every partnership we form — guided by these six principles.</p>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:var(--peach)">♿</div>
        <h3>Accessibility First</h3>
        <p>Every feature starts with accessibility at the core, not as an afterthought. If it doesn't work for everyone, it doesn't ship.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:var(--lav)">💜</div>
        <h3>Compassion</h3>
        <p>We approach every interaction — with learners, families, and partners — with genuine empathy and care. People first, always.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:var(--mint)">🤝</div>
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <p>We grow together. Learners, parents, teachers, and coaches lift each other up. No one navigates this journey alone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:#C8E6C9">🔬</div>
        <h3>Evidence-Based</h3>
        <p>Our courses and therapeutic approaches are grounded in current research, peer review, and the latest best practices in special education.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:var(--peach)">🌍</div>
        <h3>Inclusion</h3>
        <p>Diversity of ability, age, language, and background makes us stronger. We design for the edges so the center works for everyone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:var(--lav)">🔒</div>
        <h3>Trust & Safety</h3>
        <p>All our partner therapists and centers are certified. User data is protected. Every interaction on BridgeUp is safe and private.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ TEAM ══════ -->
<section class="team-section">
  <div class="team-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">The people behind it</div>
    <div class="section-title reveal">Meet the Team</div>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">A passionate group of educators, therapists, designers, and engineers — united by one purpose.</p>

    <div class="team-grid">
      <div class="team-card reveal">
        <div class="team-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--lav),var(--peach))">👩‍💻</div>
        <h3>Nour Hassan</h3>
        <div class="team-role">Founder & CEO</div>
        <div class="team-bio">Former special ed teacher turned tech founder. Has a daughter with autism — BridgeUp is personal.</div>
        <div class="team-social">
          <a class="team-soc">𝕏</a>
          <a class="team-soc">in</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card reveal">
        <div class="team-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--sky),var(--mint))">👨‍⚕️</div>
        <h3>Dr. Ahmed Samy</h3>
        <div class="team-role">Clinical Director</div>
